      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      72.3,
      526.26,
      85.75
    ],
    "text": "8. Thus, the question that arises for determination is whether the advanced age of the appellant",
    "fonts": [
