      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      272.68,
      526.03,
      285.96
    ],
    "text": "offender, whether the victim suffered any bodily harm, whether the victim was subjected",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      293.44,
      526.28,
      306.72
    ],
