    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      714.45,
      526.01,
      727.73
    ],
    "text": "puberty when she was subjected to this ordeal. Owing to her tender age, she was in no",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      735.2,
      526.18,
      748.49
    ],
