      "ArialMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      254.65,
      526.15,
      267.93
    ],
    "text": "but also the need for denunciation, deterrence, and the protection of vulnerable members",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      275.44,
      526.33,
      288.72
    ],
    "text": "of society. Accordingly, the advanced age of the appellant cannot be afforded determinative",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      296.08,
      382.63,
      309.36
    ],
    "text": "weight so as to warrant a reduction of the sentence imposed.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      316.94,
      526.26,
      348.72
    ],
    "text": "17. The minimum mandatory sentence prescribed by law for the offence of grave sexual abuse",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      356.2,
      526.3,
      369.48
    ],
