      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      397.6,
      526.38,
      410.88
    ],
    "text": "the psychological trauma she would have experienced, and the likelihood of long-lasting",
