      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      418.24,
      526.27,
      431.52
    ],
    "text": "psychological consequences in her life. Having regard to these factors, the sentence",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      438.88,
      526.29,
      452.16
    ],
    "text": "imposed falls well within the permissible statutory range. The only factors that appear to",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      459.66,
      526.08,
      472.94
    ],
    "text": "have escaped the attention of the learned trial Judge at the time of imposing the sentence",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      480.3,
      493.78,
      493.58
    ],
    "text": "are the appellant\u2019s age and the fact that he is a person with no previous convictions.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      501.16,
      526.41,
      532.94
    ],
